@startuml
title UML Class Diagram AS IS - Digisky

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor #2F5597
  ArrowColor #333333
}

class Client <<Entity>> {
  +idClient: Integer
  +name: String
  +email: String
  +company: String
}

class ServiceRequest <<Entity>> {
  +idRequest: Integer
  +requestDate: Date
  +serviceType: String
  +status: String
}

class DroneMission <<Entity>> {
  +idMission: Integer
  +missionDate: Date
  +area: String
  +operator: String
}

class SurveyData <<Entity>> {
  +idData: Integer
  +filePath: String
  +dataType: String
  +acquisitionDate: Date
}

class Report <<Entity>> {
  +idReport: Integer
  +creationDate: Date
  +format: String
  +version: String
}

class Department <<Entity>> {
  +idDepartment: Integer
  +name: String
  +role: String
  +manager: String
}

class GoogleDriveArchive <<Archive>> {
  +idArchive: Integer
  +folderName: String
  +storageType: String
  +accessPermissions: String
}

Client "1" --> "0..*" ServiceRequest : submits
ServiceRequest "1" --> "0..1" DroneMission : generates
DroneMission "1" --> "1..*" SurveyData : produces
SurveyData "1..*" --> "1" Report : used to create
Report "0..*" --> "1" GoogleDriveArchive : stored in
Department "1..*" --> "1" GoogleDriveArchive : accesses

note right of GoogleDriveArchive
AS IS issue:
unstructured storage,
manual file upload,
document duplication,
lack of centralized database.
end note

@enduml